        Description copied from interface: ParameterInfoHandler

        It could update context and state of UpdateParameterInfoContext.getObjectsToView()

        Note: context.getParameterOwner() equals to parameterOwner or null

        Note: it is executed on non UI thread.

      • updateUI

        public void updateUI(PsiAnnotationMethod p,
                     ParameterInfoUIContext context)
        Description copied from interface: ParameterInfoHandler

        This method is executed on UI thread and supposed only to update UI representation using ParameterInfoUIContext.setUIComponentEnabled(boolean) or ParameterInfoUIContext.setupUIComponentPresentation(String, int, int, boolean, boolean, boolean, Color).

        Don't perform any heavy calculations like resolve here: move it to ParameterInfoHandler.findElementForParameterInfo(CreateParameterInfoContext) or ParameterInfoHandler.updateParameterInfo(Object, UpdateParameterInfoContext).

        Specified by:
        updateUI in interface ParameterInfoHandler<PsiAnnotationParameterList,PsiAnnotationMethod>
